      <title>TikTok 禁令使 Clapper 下载量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/clapper-downloads-surge-on-tiktok-ban-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 TikTok 于 1 月 19 日面临禁令，提供短视频、直播和广播的社交媒体平台 Clapper 的下载量激增。Clapper 首席执行官 Bita Motiie 与 Sonali Basak 和 Caroline Hyde 在“彭博：市场”节目中谈论了其人气的上升。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/clapper-downloads-surge-on-tiktok-ban-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 22:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
